Class Prescription

java.lang.Object
models.Prescription
public class Prescription extends Object
The Prescription class represents a prescription entity in the system.

    • fromCSV

      public static Prescription fromCSV(String[] record)
      Creates a Prescription object from a CSV record.
      Parameters:
      record - A string array containing prescription data in the following order: [0] - Prescription ID [1] - Appointment ID [2] - Patient ID [3] - Doctor ID [4] - Medication ID [5] - Medication name [6] - Dosage [7] - Quantity [8] - Instructions [9] - Status (@see {PrescriptionStatus} enum) [10] - Date (as LocalDate)
      Returns:
      A new Prescription object populated with the CSV data
